{"tid":872593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又贏！全國政協副主席張慶黎：中國不怕貿易戰","createTime":"2018-10-22T23:08:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T01:30:47.000Z","uid":41404,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"9d82689d7ef775aa3d5af2192eb69ec782104dc3","tid":872593,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T23:08:36.000Z","msg":"中國繼續向美國特朗普政府釋出信息，表明不懼怕貿易戰。CNBC報道，全國政協第一副主席張慶黎表示，中方不會被特朗普政府脅迫。<br />\n<br />\n張慶黎周一在北京對香港美國商會25名代表說，中國從來不想與任何國家打貿易戰，更遑論是與長期戰略夥伴美國，但中國也不怕打貿易戰。中美經過幾輪磋商後，本已就貿易問題取得共識，但美國無視共識，堅持發動貿易戰並將戰爭升級，中國別無選擇，只能夠採取必要的反制行動。<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，張慶黎言論強硬，反映中美貿易戰目前看不見盡頭。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2191228/政協副主席接見美商會代表：中國不怕貿戰\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2191228%2F%E6%94%BF%E5%8D%94%E5%89%AF%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E6%8E%A5%E8%A6%8B%E7%BE%8E%E5%95%86%E6%9C%83%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%B8%8D%E6%80%95%E8%B2%BF%E6%88%B0&d=IaDdLTFpL6vYNUIIR22sNGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=23fdf061\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2191228/政協副主席接見美商會代表：中國不怕貿戰</a>"},{"pid":"a99744e3139bcff9e4a9cea1c4470f270cba9460","tid":872593,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T23:10:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ed4c7f86d9d2826f74c811ad8d7e568b6f49ede","tid":872593,"uid":50457,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T23:13:14.000Z","msg":"企硬就岩嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e1815183301efa0db47f7f9a2f71c4012a3872a","tid":872593,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike"